    of Defence supports a continuing service recovering 'missing'
    British and Commonwealth service personnel killed in conflict
    from the 1st World War right up to the Korean War in the 1950's...
    and it is this small team of six dedicated people who are providing
    Uncle Eric with the formal military funeral that he never received
